A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a sprawling neon-lit cityscape at night where glowing data streams flow like rivers between towering server buildings. In the foreground, a massive mechanical octopus made of copper pipes and circuit boards extends its tentacles across the scene, each arm connecting to different floating holographic orbs representing cloud platforms. The octopus sits atop a central hub structure pulsing with orange and teal energy. Data packets visualized as small luminescent cubes travel along the tentacles in both directions. The sky is filled with dark purple clouds pierced by vertical beams of light from the buildings below. Rain falls softly, creating reflections of the neon colors on wet metallic surfaces. The overall mood is one of complex interconnection and automated orchestration, with a sense of information flowing seamlessly between disparate systems in an industrial yet elegant dance.
